{"tid":1569745,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"市民王先生又出post表揚黨鐵喺中秋夜唔提供通宵車","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:33:56.000Z","uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b017fae33278b42417df19fb8c2d57ae7437f633","tid":1569745,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"港鐵以公眾安全為理由取消今晚的通宵列車服務，但其實通宵列車服務的存在正正就是為了保障公眾安全。<br />\n<br />\n1992年大除夕（1993年新年）慶祝過後，蘭桂坊大批市民為了趕及搭上尾班地鐵回家，最後觸發了大規模人踩人慘劇，造成21人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事後港英政府成立*獨立調查委員會*深入調查事件，報告猛烈抨擊皇家香港警察嚴重低估人潮管理風險，亦沒有預先制定災難應變措施。報告最後提出多點改善建議，其中，地鐵通宵營運，以減少特定時間大規模人流移動就是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n27年後的今天，港共以「大眾安全」為由去取消原本就是為了大眾安全而存在的措施，你是否感到相當諷刺？<br />\n<br />\n#市民王先生 #港鐵 #蘭桂坊慘劇"},{"pid":"b8cf7059a44cf024c92104e033f91c33ccdd9f0c","tid":1569745,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5994ee9b51383e64f3632c359e4c7eca6340fe18","tid":1569745,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}